1. Reiki energy healing
2. Palm Reading
3. Tarot Reading

The healing part will be followed by a New Year Celebration ritual. We will be practicing ancient technique Latihan within the post-modern mix of world music, live drumming and celestial projections. Everyone is welcome to this celebration of life, spirit and Return to Love. This meet up will include tantric boston meet up people.

7:30 - 10:30 pm
$10 - Goddess Special price
